Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.59,0:00:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要忍住  要忍住
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.02,0:00:51.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？吉野屋老师还没吃午饭吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:00:53.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,益子老师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.82,0:00:55.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什锦炒饭很美味的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.80,0:00:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.15,0:01:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本周是新学期努力奋斗之周
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.95,0:01:15.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健全的精神在于健康的饮食生活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.51,0:01:22.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃早饭胡乱减肥不仅有损于身心活力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.33,0:01:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对健康也有害无益
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.77,0:01:29.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正处于成长期的各位同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.11,0:01:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请务必好好吃饭  好好学习  尽情地运动身体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.94,0:01:47.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周的早会就讲这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.19,0:03:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二  三  四
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:52.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二  二  三  四
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.69,0:03:54.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  由乃亲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.22,0:03:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  穿短袖不冷吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.01,0:04:00.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不冷  今天很暖和的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉我迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.32,0:04:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闹钟明明响过了  但好像被我按掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.40,0:04:11.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用介意  我也是刚刚到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.24,0:04:15.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是因为肚子饿  闹钟响之前就起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.59,0:04:19.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是身体检查呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.45,0:04:22.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  要加油罗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.38,0:04:25.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要加油啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.25,0:04:27.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少也要让身高增长一些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.98,0:04:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃学姐  宫子学姐  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:33.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:35.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃莉  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.73,0:04:37.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃莉要一起做吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.61,0:04:41.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  难得换好了运动服  就做一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.00,0:04:43.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.90,0:04:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二  三  四
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:50.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二  二  三  四
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:04:52.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三  二  三  四
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.24,0:04:55.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛回到了小学时代
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.65,0:04:58.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然运动能让人神清气爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人有种“今天也要加油哦！”的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:08.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4月20日  ‘女孩子的心情’
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:26.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃亲也吃点不就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:30.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  接下来要做身体检查
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不和平时一样的话  身体检查就失去意义了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.21,0:05:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是没错  不过我果然还是会在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:39.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连由乃亲都会在意…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:55.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻学姐  振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.47,0:05:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃  真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.19,0:06:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从昨天中午开始滴食未进
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.79,0:06:04.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.11,0:06:15.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英  好甜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:21.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫  差不多该出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.13,0:06:24.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英学姐  寻学姐  先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.29,0:06:28.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪  小宫  为什么身体检查不量脚的尺码呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:39.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,22.5
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.63,0:06:42.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为量起来很麻烦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.10,0:06:43.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.20,0:06:49.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,视力下降了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:52.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.03,0:06:56.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  学姐们现在才要去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小荠怎么看上去很开心的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:03.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.25,0:07:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…因为身高有增高了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.29,0:07:11.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2mm
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:12.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是误差吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:20.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃亲  去年身高是多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.03,0:07:25.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,144.5  长高了多少呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.61,0:07:26.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  下一位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:31.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下巴不要向上抬  稍微收一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.65,0:07:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.91,0:07:36.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.76,0:07:41.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,144.3cm
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.63,0:07:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,误差  是误差吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.16,0:07:49.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  身高体重已经量好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  量好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:52.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:53.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:59.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪  你很在意体重的结果吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  完全没有胖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.73,0:08:04.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.70,0:08:06.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿身体检查表的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.14,0:08:10.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,量完体重后  遮遮掩掩地拿着表的人  基本都是在意体重的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.18,0:08:16.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年的二年级生  还有人把纸往死里折的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:18.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是寻学姐吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.59,0:08:24.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  下一位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.09,0:08:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把右眼遮起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:29.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.62,0:08:30.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:31.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.64,0:08:32.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.02,0:08:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.67,0:08:36.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.55,0:08:37.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.78,0:08:46.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这东西做三连发表演
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.47,0:08:49.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海贼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.78,0:08:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柳生十兵卫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.00,0:08:55.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独眼龙政宗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:57.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫  看上去都一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果跟去年比几乎没什么变化啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.09,0:09:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事哦  由乃同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:11.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.27,0:09:14.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有在好好成长啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.08,0:09:16.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.23,0:09:23.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能没在成长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.65,0:09:25.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  真讨厌啦  又来性骚扰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:32.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了  回去吧回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:34.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花了不少时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:37.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为全校学生都要体检嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.06,0:09:40.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻学姐  平安地到学校来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.92,0:09:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  请用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.37,0:09:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好丰盛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.91,0:09:57.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力了一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.93,0:10:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  体重变轻了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:07.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻学姐在减肥吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.11,0:10:09.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只减了一天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.78,0:10:11.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,减出效果了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:15.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过吃这么多的话又会增加的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.74,0:10:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…是那样没错啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.69,0:10:20.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:25.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来一年中  那个数字才是官方记录
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃莉  今天就请不要吐她槽了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.76,0:10:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.37,0:10:39.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉一下子放松了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.64,0:10:44.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,享受美食时的由乃亲  看上去很幸福的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫子也是一脸幸福的表情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:47.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比店里卖的要好吃多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.19,0:10:52.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点意外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:55.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我也开动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:01.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有泽学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:08.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.40,0:11:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打错电话了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.68,0:11:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  过得很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.64,0:11:16.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会  完全不会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.60,0:11:19.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点吃惊  不过很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.47,0:11:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.88,0:11:23.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家打错电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:24.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有泽学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.50,0:11:32.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…冬天时…我手机在美术教室里…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是那个捡到由乃手机的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  感觉慌慌张张的  好像是打错电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.46,0:11:42.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.77,0:11:45.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃学姐丢过手机吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.19,0:11:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年冬天  不小心忘在美术教室了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.26,0:11:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是从没忘记过东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.87,0:11:58.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手机里有许多个人情报  丢掉的话很麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经有一次忘在朋友家里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.36,0:12:09.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友也没注意  结果让她吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.01,0:12:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好是忘在朋友家里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.32,0:12:19.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我吃得这么慢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.34,0:12:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的  慢慢吃好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:23.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:28.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1月31日  ‘直言不讳’
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.71,0:12:34.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是今天在学校里拍的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.31,0:12:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在中庭的角落
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.18,0:12:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好圆啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.75,0:12:42.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鸽子呢  冷得缩着脖子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.23,0:12:44.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可爱～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.72,0:12:45.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.50,0:12:51.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次我也拍了张有趣的照片呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.36,0:12:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狗它…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.38,0:12:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狗它…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.96,0:12:59.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狗它…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:01.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狗它…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.72,0:13:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狗它到底怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.27,0:13:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  忘记手机放在哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.59,0:13:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我打个给你吧  稍微等下…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.97,0:13:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调成了震动  不会响铃音的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系哦  安静的环境里还是听得到手机的震动声响吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:29.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.84,0:13:32.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人接了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:34.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.27,0:13:38.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  嗯  您好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.16,0:13:40.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  您好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:44.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我是您拿在手的手机主人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.59,0:13:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊  真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.92,0:13:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美妙的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.37,0:13:55.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问您现在身在何处？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.41,0:13:58.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美术室？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:13:59.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:03.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  马上就去取
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.91,0:14:05.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  非常感谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.04,0:14:11.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美术室？落在学校里了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:13.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我立马就动身前去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.44,0:14:17.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  能找到真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.67,0:14:23.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但据说我的手机由于寒冷和不安而瑟瑟发抖着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于寒冷和不安？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.04,0:14:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.96,0:14:42.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有灯亮着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.10,0:14:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打搅了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:10.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事儿吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.57,0:15:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概不是没事儿的样子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.83,0:15:20.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃同学是吧  我是三年级的有泽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:22.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.28,0:15:24.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年级生…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.83,0:15:26.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  这是你的手机吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.02,0:15:33.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然间响了起来  吓了一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:36.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉心脏差点都停跳了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.39,0:15:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都画到这么晚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  现在这个时期的话  三年级生是随意去学校上课了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:56.24,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（自由登校阶段，即为在家中学习，不去学校也不算缺席的阶段。）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.41,0:16:00.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实现阶段不得不去研究所的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:03.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为讨厌战战兢兢的生活  于是就翘掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:06.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究所…辟辟啪啪的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.10,0:16:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有电流的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.34,0:16:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亦或是盐酸浴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.81,0:16:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究所说的是预备学校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:21.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美术科的预备学校也常常被叫做研究所呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.15,0:16:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正在进行考前讲座
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.05,0:16:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氛围可是超级紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.60,0:16:33.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  做我的人体模特儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.27,0:16:37.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微转换下心情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.04,0:16:38.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.25,0:16:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.53,0:16:47.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就快点脱吧“啪”地脱得精精光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是我们学科的老笑话了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.08,0:17:11.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身子可以不用那么僵硬的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:17.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说讲完电话后  你很快就过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.67,0:17:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住得很近吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:23.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  就是正对学校的那个公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.62,0:17:26.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在暖阳庄的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.72,0:17:27.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:31.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个疯丫头公寓的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来还有这种叫法的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.84,0:17:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究所离这边很远吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.40,0:17:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在下一站  也不是很远
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.34,0:17:46.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但怎么说到家也会晚些
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.56,0:17:48.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会晚到什么程度呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.83,0:17:52.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到家都差不多要9点了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.41,0:17:59.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也准备考美术大学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.20,0:18:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应…应该会考吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.41,0:18:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有泽学姐上了大学后打算做些什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.58,0:18:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没决定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.88,0:18:21.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年秋天的时候去逛了Open campus
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.84,0:18:26.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全被征服了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:29.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然年龄不过大我两三岁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.87,0:18:31.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不论作品的质量也好  搭配方式也好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.99,0:18:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我完全不是一个档次上的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.02,0:18:37.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是既帅气又耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:41.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是呢就觉得“啊  真想考进这所学校”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:44.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“在那里磨练自己”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:46.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时是这么觉得的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.77,0:18:52.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.53,0:18:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是粗稿  要看下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.64,0:18:58.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.26,0:19:10.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画得好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:12.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却不仅仅是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.20,0:19:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活灵活现的  感觉好温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是美妙的画
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.77,0:19:27.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉  说了些自以为是的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.91,0:19:30.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事…我并没有生气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉  让你陪我到这么晚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有的事  这段时间很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.55,0:19:45.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是  许久没有如此快乐地沉浸在绘画之中了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.29,0:19:46.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.44,0:19:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.02,0:19:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.40,0:19:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考试  请加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.77,0:20:05.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.01,0:20:26.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话？是沙英学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.10,0:20:27.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.30,0:20:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  由乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:33.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  这么晚了我们都很担心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.52,0:20:34.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.20,0:20:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在疯丫头公寓的门前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.86,0:20:42.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挂了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.93,0:20:48.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在学校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.11,0:20:53.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.76,0:20:56.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.88,0:20:59.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉让你们担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.09,0:21:01.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,0:21:03.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎由乃亲和手机一起回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.99,0:21:04.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.35,0:21:07.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到手机真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:09.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.51,0:21:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等下下…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.06,0:21:28.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  小狗呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:30.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在说什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:46.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能找到手机真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.45,0:21:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有泽学姐真是好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.75,0:21:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还会再见到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.19,0:22:05.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝愿能考入美术大学
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.89,0:22:10.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1月31日  ‘完’  待续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.66,0:23:44.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次在便利店里被店员握住了手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.34,0:23:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会有这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.50,0:23:46.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找零的时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.90,0:23:48.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人提心吊胆的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.93,0:23:50.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便问下  是右手还是左手？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.60,0:23:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有过双手都被握住的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.20,0:23:56.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这在寒冷的季节里还是会很高兴的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.24,0:23:58.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一话是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.95,0:24:02.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‘10月15日  天空的高度也好  树丛的阴影也罢’
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.55,0:24:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‘4月26日～27日  恋爱达人’
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.49,0:24:07.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在山吹高中里等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.09,0:24:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要来看哟
